OL,3,CCheaper for Britons to rent than buy
OL,4,Cafter mortgage rates rise 'sharply'
OL,6,FIt has become cheaper to rent a home
OL,7,Fin Britain than to buy, following a
OL,8,Fsharp rise in mortgage rates since the
OL,9,Fwar in Iran, new figures show.
OL,11,FThe cost of a typical new mortgage
OL,12,Fpayment has overtaken the average rent
OL,13,Ffor the first time since June last
OL,14,Fyear, according to analysis by
OL,15,FRightmove.
OL,17,FIt found the average advertised
OL,18,Fmonthly rent across Britain is
OL,19,Fcurrently #1,547.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
