CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777521849
OL,3,CCheaper for Britons to rent than buy
OL,4,Cafter mortgage rates rise 'sharply'
OL,6,FThis was #123 lower than the average
OL,7,Fnew monthly mortgage payment of #1,670.
OL,9,FRightmove's mortgage figure is based
OL,10,Fon the current average asking price
OL,11,Ffor a home of #373,971 and the average
OL,12,Ftwo-year fixed rate in April so far.
OL,13,FIt also assumes a buyer has a 20%
OL,14,Fdeposit and a 30-year term to pay off
OL,15,Ftheir mortgage.
OL,17,FThe shift has been driven by borrowing
OL,18,Fcosts moving higher since the
OL,19,Fbeginning of March, when conflict
OL,20,Fescalated in the Middle East.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
