OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777521849
OL,3,CCheaper for Britons to rent than buy
OL,4,Cafter mortgage rates rise 'sharply'
OL,6,FThis led to swap rates, which are used
OL,7,Fby lenders to price mortgages, to rise
OL,8,Famid volatility in the financial
OL,9,Fmarkets, prompting lenders to pull a
OL,10,Fswathe of mortgage deals from the
OL,11,Fmarket.
OL,13,FAs a result, the average two-year
OL,14,Ffixed mortgage rate has increased from
OL,15,F4.24% in February to 5.35% in April,
OL,16,FRightmove said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
