OL,3,CCheaper for Britons to rent than buy
OL,4,Cafter mortgage rates rise 'sharply'
OL,6,FHowever, a wave of banks and building
OL,7,Fsocieties have been cutting their
OL,8,Frates in the past few days in a sign
OL,9,Fof more positive sentiment entering
OL,10,Fthe market.
OL,12,FColleen Babcock, Rightmove's property
OL,13,Fexpert, said: "Mortgage payments have
OL,14,Frisen quite sharply in a short space
OL,15,Fof time for new buyers.
OL,26,@uD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
