PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777521849
OL,3,CCheaper for Britons to rent than buy
OL,4,Cafter mortgage rates rise 'sharply'
OL,6,F"It will be interesting to see whether
OL,7,Fmore wouldbe buyers turn to renting
OL,8,Ftemporarily while rates remain high,
OL,9,Fparticularly when monthly costs can
OL,10,Fexceed average rents and the timing of
OL,11,Frate cuts is still unclear."
OL,13,FRightmove's analysis shows that while
OL,14,Frenting is cheaper than a mortgage on
OL,15,Faverage across Britain, this is not
OL,16,Fthe case for Scotland and the North
OL,17,FEast, where it remains cheaper to buy.
OL,19,FThe gap between rents and mortgage
OL,20,Fpayments also varies significantly in
OL,21,Fdifferent regions of Britain.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
