OL,3,CCheaper for Britons to rent than buy
OL,4,Cafter mortgage rates rise 'sharply'
OL,6,FIn the South East, the average monthly
OL,7,Frent is #304 less than the average
OL,8,Fmortgage payment. This rises to #362
OL,9,Fin London.
OL,11,FIn comparison, in the North West it is
OL,12,F#7 cheaper to rent than buy, according
OL,13,Fto the analysis.
OL,15,FFurthermore, factors such as buying a
OL,16,Fhome with a larger deposit, borrowing
OL,17,Fless from the bank or spreading
OL,18,Fpayments over a longer period can all
OL,19,Flower monthly mortgage costs on an
OL,20,Findividual basis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
