FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777521849
OL,3,CCheaper for Britons to rent than buy
OL,4,Cafter mortgage rates rise 'sharply'
OL,6,FNathan Emerson, chief executive of
OL,7,FPropertymark, said: "This shift
OL,8,Fhighlights the wider economic
OL,9,Fpressures facing consumers, where
OL,10,Faffordability challenges are being
OL,11,Ffelt across both renting and buying.
OL,13,F"While renting may appear
OL,14,Fcomparatively cheaper in the short
OL,15,Fterm, it does not necessarily mean it
OL,16,Fis more affordable overall,
OL,17,Fparticularly as tenants continue to
OL,18,Fmanage the cost of living and limited
OL,19,Fhousing supply."
OL,26,@oD@UOUuD@AOU{D@PO]
